}}'''DR Congo''' (Democratic Republic of Congo) is a [[Nations|country]] that was released on BitLife in December 2019. Its default cities are the capital, Kinshasa along with Lubumbashi and Mbuji-Mayi.

In December 2019 on iOS; new countries were added. Along with DR Congo; there was also Austria, Bahamas, Costa Rica, Kazakhstan, Kenya, Kuwait, Lebanon, Mongolia, Nepal, Ukraine, and Vietnam. This was added in the ''Friends'' Update.

